Hi,

I'm using Ocamlbuild to build a project, and would very much like to use it
to generate the Ocamldoc API documentation as well.  Problem is, by default
Ocamlbuild can't handle docs contained in implementation files, and doesn't
know anything about docs in external txt files (useful for writing tutorial=
s
such as those in Ocamlnet).

So, before I embark on reinventing the wheel, my question is if someone has
already written a plugin to handle the tasks above.  Anyone?

